  "description": "Reception statistics from the edge-sdr receivers, persisted in Prometheus (the dump1090-fa / AIS-catcher web UIs lose history on pod restart). Data flows: receiver \u2192 prometheus-agent-edge-sdr \u2192 remote_write \u2192 production Prometheus.",
